We figured that our languages work similarly... [Black Speakerman]:

Try it... [POV Speakerman]:

[TRUMPETS OF DOMINANCE PLAY] Fools... *rip robert* You have no idea who's coming ;) F O R G I V E    M E I    H A V E    B E C O M E Y O U R    D O O M Fascinating... *sounds of agony* Choke your grief... Cosmos hears no cries... Only power speaks. [POV Speakerman]:
No... NO! [POV Speakerman]:
You have to leave! [POV Speakerman]:
Please...
